question: calculate the number of patients who were diagnosed with awaiting organ transplant status and did not return to the hospital within 2 month this year.
template: count the number of patients who did not come back to the hospital within 2 month after diagnosed with awaiting organ transplant status this year.
query: select ( select count( distinct t1.subject_id ) from ( select admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime from diagnoses_icd join admissions on diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id where diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( select d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code from d_icd_diagnoses where d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'awaiting organ transplant status' ) and datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) as t1 ) - ( select count( distinct t2.subject_id ) from ( select admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime from diagnoses_icd join admissions on diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id where diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( select d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code from d_icd_diagnoses where d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'awaiting organ transplant status' ) and datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) as t2 join admissions on t2.subject_id = admissions.subject_id where t2.charttime < admissions.admittime and datetime(admissions.admittime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') and datetime(admissions.admittime) between datetime(t2.charttime) and datetime(t2.charttime,'+2 month') )

value.diagnosis_name: awaiting organ transplant status

q_tag: count the number of patients who did not come back to the hospital [time_filter_within] after diagnosed with {diagnosis_name} [time_filter_global1].
tag: Count the number of patients who did not come back to the hospital [time_filter_within:within-n_month] after diagnosed with {diagnosis_name} [time_filter_global1:rel-year-this].

query: select d_labitems.label from d_labitems where d_labitems.itemid in ( select t3.itemid from ( select t2.itemid, dense_rank() over ( order by count(*) desc ) as c1 from ( select admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id from procedures_icd join admissions on procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id where procedures_icd.icd_code = ( select d_icd_procedures.icd_code from d_icd_procedures where d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'fluoroscopy of multiple coronary arteries using high osmolar contrast' ) and strftime('%y',procedures_icd.charttime) <= '2101' ) as t1 join ( select admissions.subject_id, labevents.itemid, labevents.charttime, admissions.hadm_id from labevents join admissions on labevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id where strftime('%y',labevents.charttime) <= '2101' ) as t2 on t1.subject_id = t2.subject_id where t1.charttime < t2.charttime and t1.hadm_id = t2.hadm_id group by t2.itemid ) as t3 where t3.c1 <= 5 )

value.procedure_name: fluoroscopy of multiple coronary arteries using high osmolar contrast

question: what is the two year survival rate of patients who were prescribed sodium chloride 0.9% after having been diagnosed with unspecified fracture of navicular [scaphoid] bone of left wrist, initial encounter for open fracture?

query: select sum( case when patients.dod is null then 1 when strftime('%j',patients.dod) - strftime('%j',t4.charttime) > 2 * 365 then 1 else 0 end ) * 100 / count(*) from ( select t2.subject_id, t2.charttime from ( select t1.subject_id, t1.charttime from ( select admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime from diagnoses_icd join admissions on diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id where diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( select d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code from d_icd_diagnoses where d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'unspecified fracture of navicular [scaphoid] bone of left wrist, initial encounter for open fracture' ) group by admissions.subject_id having min(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) as t1 where strftime('%j',current_time) - strftime('%j',t1.charttime) > 2 * 365 ) as t2 join ( select admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime from prescriptions join admissions on prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id where prescriptions.drug = 'sodium chloride 0.9%' ) as t3 on t2.subject_id = t3.subject_id where t2.charttime < t3.starttime ) as t4 join patients on t4.subject_id = patients.subject_id

query: select t3.drug from ( select t2.drug, dense_rank() over ( order by count(*) desc ) as c1 from ( select admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id from diagnoses_icd join admissions on diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id where diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( select d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code from d_icd_diagnoses where d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'atherosclerotic heart disease of native coronary artery with unstable angina pectoris' ) and strftime('%y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= '2104' ) as t1 join ( select admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, admissions.hadm_id from prescriptions join admissions on prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id where admissions.age between 50 and 59 and strftime('%y',prescriptions.starttime) >= '2104' ) as t2 on t1.subject_id = t2.subject_id where t1.charttime < t2.starttime and t1.hadm_id = t2.hadm_id group by t2.drug ) as t3 where t3.c1 <= 4

value.diagnosis_name: atherosclerotic heart disease of native coronary artery with unstable angina pectoris

question: what was the top five diagnosis with the highest four year mortality rate?

question: calculate the four year survival rate of those who were diagnosed with other antihypertensive agents causing adverse effects in therapeutic use.
template: what is the four year survival rate of patients diagnosed with other antihypertensive agents causing adverse effects in therapeutic use?
query: select sum( case when patients.dod is null then 1 when strftime('%j',patients.dod) - strftime('%j',t2.charttime) > 4 * 365 then 1 else 0 end ) * 100 / count(*) from ( select t1.subject_id, t1.charttime from ( select admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime from diagnoses_icd join admissions on diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id where diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( select d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code from d_icd_diagnoses where d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'other antihypertensive agents causing adverse effects in therapeutic use' ) group by admissions.subject_id having min(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) as t1 where strftime('%j',current_time) - strftime('%j',t1.charttime) > 4 * 365 ) as t2 join patients on t2.subject_id = patients.subject_id

value.diagnosis_name: other antihypertensive agents causing adverse effects in therapeutic use

question: what is the one year survival rate of renal dialysis status patients who were prescribed with propofol?
template: what is the one year survival rate of patients who were prescribed propofol after having been diagnosed with renal dialysis status?
query: select sum( case when patients.dod is null then 1 when strftime('%j',patients.dod) - strftime('%j',t4.charttime) > 1 * 365 then 1 else 0 end ) * 100 / count(*) from ( select t2.subject_id, t2.charttime from ( select t1.subject_id, t1.charttime from ( select admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime from diagnoses_icd join admissions on diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id where diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( select d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code from d_icd_diagnoses where d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'renal dialysis status' ) group by admissions.subject_id having min(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) as t1 where strftime('%j',current_time) - strftime('%j',t1.charttime) > 1 * 365 ) as t2 join ( select admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime from prescriptions join admissions on prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id where prescriptions.drug = 'propofol' ) as t3 on t2.subject_id = t3.subject_id where t2.charttime < t3.starttime ) as t4 join patients on t4.subject_id = patients.subject_id

value.diagnosis_name: renal dialysis status

query: select count( distinct t1.subject_id ) from ( select admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id from diagnoses_icd join admissions on diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id where diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( select d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code from d_icd_diagnoses where d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'hyperosmolality and hypernatremia' ) ) as t1 join ( select admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id from procedures_icd join admissions on procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id where procedures_icd.icd_code = ( select d_icd_procedures.icd_code from d_icd_procedures where d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'left heart cardiac catheterization' ) ) as t2 on t1.subject_id = t2.subject_id where t1.charttime < t2.charttime and t1.hadm_id = t2.hadm_id

value.diagnosis_name: hyperosmolality and hypernatremia
value.procedure_name: left heart cardiac catheterization

question: how many patients had they had insertion of pacemaker, dual chamber into chest subcutaneous tissue and fascia, open approach within 2 month after they were diagnosed with chronic obstructive asthma, unspecified in 2103?
template: count the number of patients who received a insertion of pacemaker, dual chamber into chest subcutaneous tissue and fascia, open approach procedure within 2 month after having been diagnosed with chronic obstructive asthma, unspecified in 2103.
query: select count( distinct t1.subject_id ) from ( select admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime from diagnoses_icd join admissions on diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id where diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( select d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code from d_icd_diagnoses where d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'chronic obstructive asthma, unspecified' ) and strftime('%y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2103' ) as t1 join ( select admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime from procedures_icd join admissions on procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id where procedures_icd.icd_code = ( select d_icd_procedures.icd_code from d_icd_procedures where d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'insertion of pacemaker, dual chamber into chest subcutaneous tissue and fascia, open approach' ) and strftime('%y',procedures_icd.charttime) = '2103' ) as t2 on t1.subject_id = t2.subject_id where t1.charttime < t2.charttime and datetime(t2.charttime) between datetime(t1.charttime) and datetime(t1.charttime,'+2 month')

value.diagnosis_name: chronic obstructive asthma, unspecified
value.procedure_name: insertion of pacemaker, dual chamber into chest subcutaneous tissue and fascia, open approach

question: what is the one year survival rate of other osteomyelitis, ankle and foot patients diagnosed?
template: what is the one year survival rate of patients diagnosed with other osteomyelitis, ankle and foot?
query: select sum( case when patients.dod is null then 1 when strftime('%j',patients.dod) - strftime('%j',t2.charttime) > 1 * 365 then 1 else 0 end ) * 100 / count(*) from ( select t1.subject_id, t1.charttime from ( select admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime from diagnoses_icd join admissions on diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id where diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( select d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code from d_icd_diagnoses where d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'other osteomyelitis, ankle and foot' ) group by admissions.subject_id having min(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) as t1 where strftime('%j',current_time) - strftime('%j',t1.charttime) > 1 * 365 ) as t2 join patients on t2.subject_id = patients.subject_id

value.diagnosis_name: other osteomyelitis, ankle and foot

query: select count( distinct t1.subject_id ) from ( select admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime from diagnoses_icd join admissions on diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id where diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( select d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code from d_icd_diagnoses where d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'chronic airway obstruction, not elsewhere classified' ) and datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-2 year') ) as t1 join ( select admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime from prescriptions join admissions on prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id where prescriptions.drug = 'multivitamins' and datetime(prescriptions.starttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-2 year') ) as t2 on t1.subject_id = t2.subject_id where t1.charttime < t2.starttime and datetime(t2.starttime) between datetime(t1.charttime) and datetime(t1.charttime,'+2 month')

value.diagnosis_name: chronic airway obstruction, not elsewhere classified

question: what were the four diagnoses that have the lowest four year survival rate?
template: what are the top four diagnoses that have the highest four year mortality rate?
query: select d_icd_diagnoses.long_title from d_icd_diagnoses where d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code in ( select t4.icd_code from ( select t3.icd_code, dense_rank() over ( order by t3.c1 desc ) as c2 from ( select t2.icd_code, 100 - sum( case when patients.dod is null then 1 when strftime('%j',patients.dod) - strftime('%j',t2.charttime) > 4 * 365 then 1 else 0 end ) * 100 / count(*) as c1 from ( select t1.subject_id, t1.icd_code, t1.charttime from ( select admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime from admissions join diagnoses_icd on admissions.hadm_id = diagnoses_icd.hadm_id group by admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code having min(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) as t1 where strftime('%j',current_time) - strftime('%j',t1.charttime) > 4 * 365 ) as t2 join patients on t2.subject_id = patients.subject_id group by t2.icd_code ) as t3 ) as t4 where t4.c2 <= 4 )
q_tag: what are the top [n_rank] diagnoses that have the highest [n_survival_period] mortality rate?

question: count the number of patients who were diagnosed with umbilical hernia without mention of obstruction or gangrene and didn't return to the hospital within 2 month until 2 year ago.
template: count the number of patients who did not come back to the hospital within 2 month after diagnosed with umbilical hernia without mention of obstruction or gangrene until 2 year ago.
query: select ( select count( distinct t1.subject_id ) from ( select admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime from diagnoses_icd join admissions on diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id where diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( select d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code from d_icd_diagnoses where d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'umbilical hernia without mention of obstruction or gangrene' ) and datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime) <= datetime(current_time,'-2 year') ) as t1 ) - ( select count( distinct t2.subject_id ) from ( select admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime from diagnoses_icd join admissions on diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id where diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( select d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code from d_icd_diagnoses where d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'umbilical hernia without mention of obstruction or gangrene' ) and datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime) <= datetime(current_time,'-2 year') ) as t2 join admissions on t2.subject_id = admissions.subject_id where t2.charttime < admissions.admittime and datetime(admissions.admittime) <= datetime(current_time,'-2 year') and datetime(admissions.admittime) between datetime(t2.charttime) and datetime(t2.charttime,'+2 month') )

value.diagnosis_name: umbilical hernia without mention of obstruction or gangrene

query: select d_labitems.label from d_labitems where d_labitems.itemid in ( select t3.itemid from ( select t2.itemid, dense_rank() over ( order by count(*) desc ) as c1 from ( select admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id from diagnoses_icd join admissions on diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id where diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( select d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code from d_icd_diagnoses where d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'acute upper respiratory infection, unspecified' ) and strftime('%y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2103' ) as t1 join ( select admissions.subject_id, labevents.itemid, labevents.charttime, admissions.hadm_id from labevents join admissions on labevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id where strftime('%y',labevents.charttime) = '2103' ) as t2 on t1.subject_id = t2.subject_id where t1.charttime < t2.charttime and t1.hadm_id = t2.hadm_id group by t2.itemid ) as t3 where t3.c1 <= 4 )

value.diagnosis_name: acute upper respiratory infection, unspecified

question: what's the top three diagnosis that had the highest two year mortality rate?
template: what are the top three diagnoses that have the highest two year mortality rate?
query: select d_icd_diagnoses.long_title from d_icd_diagnoses where d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code in ( select t4.icd_code from ( select t3.icd_code, dense_rank() over ( order by t3.c1 desc ) as c2 from ( select t2.icd_code, 100 - sum( case when patients.dod is null then 1 when strftime('%j',patients.dod) - strftime('%j',t2.charttime) > 2 * 365 then 1 else 0 end ) * 100 / count(*) as c1 from ( select t1.subject_id, t1.icd_code, t1.charttime from ( select admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime from admissions join diagnoses_icd on admissions.hadm_id = diagnoses_icd.hadm_id group by admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code having min(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) as t1 where strftime('%j',current_time) - strftime('%j',t1.charttime) > 2 * 365 ) as t2 join patients on t2.subject_id = patients.subject_id group by t2.icd_code ) as t3 ) as t4 where t4.c2 <= 3 )
q_tag: what are the top [n_rank] diagnoses that have the highest [n_survival_period] mortality rate?

query: select d_icd_diagnoses.long_title from d_icd_diagnoses where d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code in ( select t4.icd_code from ( select t3.icd_code, dense_rank() over ( order by t3.c1 desc ) as c2 from ( select t2.icd_code, 100 - sum( case when patients.dod is null then 1 when strftime('%j',patients.dod) - strftime('%j',t2.charttime) > 1 * 365 then 1 else 0 end ) * 100 / count(*) as c1 from ( select t1.subject_id, t1.icd_code, t1.charttime from ( select admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime from admissions join diagnoses_icd on admissions.hadm_id = diagnoses_icd.hadm_id group by admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code having min(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) as t1 where strftime('%j',current_time) - strftime('%j',t1.charttime) > 1 * 365 ) as t2 join patients on t2.subject_id = patients.subject_id group by t2.icd_code ) as t3 ) as t4 where t4.c2 <= 3 )
q_tag: what are the top [n_rank] diagnoses that have the highest [n_survival_period] mortality rate?
tag: What are the top [n_rank:three] diagnoses that have the highest [n_survival_period:one year] mortality rate?

question: what was the two year survival rate of thalassemia minor patients who were prescribed with levofloxacin?
template: what is the two year survival rate of patients who were prescribed levofloxacin after having been diagnosed with thalassemia minor?
query: select sum( case when patients.dod is null then 1 when strftime('%j',patients.dod) - strftime('%j',t4.charttime) > 2 * 365 then 1 else 0 end ) * 100 / count(*) from ( select t2.subject_id, t2.charttime from ( select t1.subject_id, t1.charttime from ( select admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime from diagnoses_icd join admissions on diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id where diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( select d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code from d_icd_diagnoses where d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'thalassemia minor' ) group by admissions.subject_id having min(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) as t1 where strftime('%j',current_time) - strftime('%j',t1.charttime) > 2 * 365 ) as t2 join ( select admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime from prescriptions join admissions on prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id where prescriptions.drug = 'levofloxacin' ) as t3 on t2.subject_id = t3.subject_id where t2.charttime < t3.starttime ) as t4 join patients on t4.subject_id = patients.subject_id

value.diagnosis_name: thalassemia minor

query: select count( distinct t1.subject_id ) from ( select admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime from diagnoses_icd join admissions on diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id where diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( select d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code from d_icd_diagnoses where d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'long term (current) use of insulin' ) and datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-1 year') ) as t1 join ( select admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime from procedures_icd join admissions on procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id where procedures_icd.icd_code = ( select d_icd_procedures.icd_code from d_icd_procedures where d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'insertion of non-drug-eluting peripheral (non-coronary) vessel stent(s)' ) and datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-1 year') ) as t2 on t1.subject_id = t2.subject_id where t1.charttime < t2.charttime and datetime(t2.charttime) between datetime(t1.charttime) and datetime(t1.charttime,'+2 month')

value.diagnosis_name: long term (current) use of insulin
value.procedure_name: insertion of non-drug-eluting peripheral (non-coronary) vessel stent(s)

query: select d_icd_procedures.long_title from d_icd_procedures where d_icd_procedures.icd_code in ( select t3.icd_code from ( select t2.icd_code, dense_rank() over ( order by count(*) desc ) as c1 from ( select admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id from diagnoses_icd join admissions on diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id where diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( select d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code from d_icd_diagnoses where d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'septicemia due to anaerobes' ) and strftime('%y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= '2103' ) as t1 join ( select admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.icd_code, procedures_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id from procedures_icd join admissions on procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id where strftime('%y',procedures_icd.charttime) >= '2103' ) as t2 on t1.subject_id = t2.subject_id where t1.charttime < t2.charttime and t1.hadm_id = t2.hadm_id group by t2.icd_code ) as t3 where t3.c1 <= 5 )

value.diagnosis_name: septicemia due to anaerobes

question: tell me the top five diagnosis that has the highest three year mortality rate?
template: what are the top five diagnoses that have the highest three year mortality rate?
query: select d_icd_diagnoses.long_title from d_icd_diagnoses where d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code in ( select t4.icd_code from ( select t3.icd_code, dense_rank() over ( order by t3.c1 desc ) as c2 from ( select t2.icd_code, 100 - sum( case when patients.dod is null then 1 when strftime('%j',patients.dod) - strftime('%j',t2.charttime) > 3 * 365 then 1 else 0 end ) * 100 / count(*) as c1 from ( select t1.subject_id, t1.icd_code, t1.charttime from ( select admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime from admissions join diagnoses_icd on admissions.hadm_id = diagnoses_icd.hadm_id group by admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code having min(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) as t1 where strftime('%j',current_time) - strftime('%j',t1.charttime) > 3 * 365 ) as t2 join patients on t2.subject_id = patients.subject_id group by t2.icd_code ) as t3 ) as t4 where t4.c2 <= 5 )
q_tag: what are the top [n_rank] diagnoses that have the highest [n_survival_period] mortality rate?
tag: What are the top [n_rank:five] diagnoses that have the highest [n_survival_period:three year] mortality rate?

question: what is the five year survival rate of malignant neoplasm of lower lobe, right bronchus or lung patients who were prescribed with mycophenolate mofetil?
template: what is the five year survival rate of patients who were prescribed mycophenolate mofetil after having been diagnosed with malignant neoplasm of lower lobe, right bronchus or lung?
query: select sum( case when patients.dod is null then 1 when strftime('%j',patients.dod) - strftime('%j',t4.charttime) > 5 * 365 then 1 else 0 end ) * 100 / count(*) from ( select t2.subject_id, t2.charttime from ( select t1.subject_id, t1.charttime from ( select admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime from diagnoses_icd join admissions on diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id where diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( select d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code from d_icd_diagnoses where d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'malignant neoplasm of lower lobe, right bronchus or lung' ) group by admissions.subject_id having min(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) as t1 where strftime('%j',current_time) - strftime('%j',t1.charttime) > 5 * 365 ) as t2 join ( select admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime from prescriptions join admissions on prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id where prescriptions.drug = 'mycophenolate mofetil' ) as t3 on t2.subject_id = t3.subject_id where t2.charttime < t3.starttime ) as t4 join patients on t4.subject_id = patients.subject_id

value.diagnosis_name: malignant neoplasm of lower lobe, right bronchus or lung

query: select d_labitems.label from d_labitems where d_labitems.itemid in ( select t3.itemid from ( select t2.itemid, dense_rank() over ( order by count(*) desc ) as c1 from ( select admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime from diagnoses_icd join admissions on diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id where diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( select d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code from d_icd_diagnoses where d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'hypotension, unspecified' ) and datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-4 year') ) as t1 join ( select admissions.subject_id, labevents.itemid, labevents.charttime from labevents join admissions on labevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id where datetime(labevents.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-4 year') ) as t2 on t1.subject_id = t2.subject_id where t1.charttime < t2.charttime and datetime(t1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(t2.charttime,'start of month') group by t2.itemid ) as t3 where t3.c1 <= 4 )

value.diagnosis_name: hypotension, unspecified

question: what are the two year survival rates for those who were prescribed sumatriptan succinate after having been diagnosed with multiple involvement of mitral and aortic valves?
template: what is the two year survival rate of patients who were prescribed sumatriptan succinate after having been diagnosed with multiple involvement of mitral and aortic valves?
query: select sum( case when patients.dod is null then 1 when strftime('%j',patients.dod) - strftime('%j',t4.charttime) > 2 * 365 then 1 else 0 end ) * 100 / count(*) from ( select t2.subject_id, t2.charttime from ( select t1.subject_id, t1.charttime from ( select admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime from diagnoses_icd join admissions on diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id where diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( select d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code from d_icd_diagnoses where d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'multiple involvement of mitral and aortic valves' ) group by admissions.subject_id having min(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) as t1 where strftime('%j',current_time) - strftime('%j',t1.charttime) > 2 * 365 ) as t2 join ( select admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime from prescriptions join admissions on prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id where prescriptions.drug = 'sumatriptan succinate' ) as t3 on t2.subject_id = t3.subject_id where t2.charttime < t3.starttime ) as t4 join patients on t4.subject_id = patients.subject_id

value.diagnosis_name: multiple involvement of mitral and aortic valves

query: select min(t1.c1) from ( select sum(cost.cost) as c1 from cost where cost.hadm_id in ( select labevents.hadm_id from labevents where labevents.itemid in ( select d_labitems.itemid from d_labitems where d_labitems.label = 'urine creatinine' ) ) and strftime('%y',cost.chargetime) = '2103' group by cost.hadm_id ) as t1
q_tag: what is_verb the [agg_function] total hospital cost that involves a {lab_name} lab test [time_filter_global1]?
tag: What is_verb the [agg_function:minimum] total hospital cost that involves a {lab_name} lab test [time_filter_global1:abs-year-in]?

question: what were the three most frequent diagnoses that patients were diagnosed with within the same month after the diagnosis of physical restraint status in 2105?

query: select d_icd_diagnoses.long_title from d_icd_diagnoses where d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code in ( select t3.icd_code from ( select t2.icd_code, dense_rank() over ( order by count(*) desc ) as c1 from ( select admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime from diagnoses_icd join admissions on diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id where diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( select d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code from d_icd_diagnoses where d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'physical restraint status' ) and strftime('%y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2105' ) as t1 join ( select admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime from diagnoses_icd join admissions on diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id where strftime('%y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2105' ) as t2 on t1.subject_id = t2.subject_id where t1.charttime < t2.charttime and datetime(t1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(t2.charttime,'start of month') group by t2.icd_code ) as t3 where t3.c1 <= 3 )

question: what are the two year survival rates for those who were prescribed albuterol inhaler after having been diagnosed with duodenal ulcer, unspecified as acute or chronic, without hemorrhage or perforation, without mention of obstruction?
template: what is the two year survival rate of patients who were prescribed albuterol inhaler after having been diagnosed with duodenal ulcer, unspecified as acute or chronic, without hemorrhage or perforation, without mention of obstruction?
query: select sum( case when patients.dod is null then 1 when strftime('%j',patients.dod) - strftime('%j',t4.charttime) > 2 * 365 then 1 else 0 end ) * 100 / count(*) from ( select t2.subject_id, t2.charttime from ( select t1.subject_id, t1.charttime from ( select admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime from diagnoses_icd join admissions on diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id where diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( select d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code from d_icd_diagnoses where d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'duodenal ulcer, unspecified as acute or chronic, without hemorrhage or perforation, without mention of obstruction' ) group by admissions.subject_id having min(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) as t1 where strftime('%j',current_time) - strftime('%j',t1.charttime) > 2 * 365 ) as t2 join ( select admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime from prescriptions join admissions on prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id where prescriptions.drug = 'albuterol inhaler' ) as t3 on t2.subject_id = t3.subject_id where t2.charttime < t3.starttime ) as t4 join patients on t4.subject_id = patients.subject_id

question: among the patients who were diagnosed with gross hematuria tell me the one year survival rate.
template: what is the one year survival rate of patients diagnosed with gross hematuria?
query: select sum( case when patients.dod is null then 1 when strftime('%j',patients.dod) - strftime('%j',t2.charttime) > 1 * 365 then 1 else 0 end ) * 100 / count(*) from ( select t1.subject_id, t1.charttime from ( select admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime from diagnoses_icd join admissions on diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id where diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( select d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code from d_icd_diagnoses where d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'gross hematuria' ) group by admissions.subject_id having min(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) as t1 where strftime('%j',current_time) - strftime('%j',t1.charttime) > 1 * 365 ) as t2 join patients on t2.subject_id = patients.subject_id

value.diagnosis_name: gross hematuria

query: select d_labitems.label from d_labitems where d_labitems.itemid in ( select t1.itemid from ( select labevents.itemid, dense_rank() over ( order by count(*) desc ) as c1 from labevents where labevents.hadm_id in ( select admissions.hadm_id from admissions where admissions.age between 50 and 59 ) and strftime('%y',labevents.charttime) = '2101' group by labevents.itemid ) as t1 where t1.c1 <= 4 )

question: what are the two year survival rates for dependence on wheelchair patients?
template: what is the two year survival rate of patients diagnosed with dependence on wheelchair?
query: select sum( case when patients.dod is null then 1 when strftime('%j',patients.dod) - strftime('%j',t2.charttime) > 2 * 365 then 1 else 0 end ) * 100 / count(*) from ( select t1.subject_id, t1.charttime from ( select admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime from diagnoses_icd join admissions on diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id where diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( select d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code from d_icd_diagnoses where d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'dependence on wheelchair' ) group by admissions.subject_id having min(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) as t1 where strftime('%j',current_time) - strftime('%j',t1.charttime) > 2 * 365 ) as t2 join patients on t2.subject_id = patients.subject_id

value.diagnosis_name: dependence on wheelchair

q_tag: what is the [n_survival_period] survival rate of patients diagnosed with {diagnosis_name}?
tag: What is the [n_survival_period:two year] survival rate of patients diagnosed with {diagnosis_name}?

question: count the number of people that died after being diagnosed with diarrhea within 2 month last year.
template: count the number of patients who were dead after having been diagnosed with diarrhea within 2 month last year.
query: select count( distinct t2.subject_id ) from ( select t1.subject_id, t1.charttime from ( select admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime from admissions join diagnoses_icd on admissions.hadm_id = diagnoses_icd.hadm_id where diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( select d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code from d_icd_diagnoses where d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'diarrhea' ) ) as t1 group by t1.subject_id having min(t1.charttime) = t1.charttime and datetime(t1.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-1 year') ) as t2 join ( select patients.subject_id, admissions.hadm_id, patients.dod from admissions join patients on patients.subject_id = admissions.subject_id where patients.dod is not null and datetime(patients.dod,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-1 year') ) as t3 on t2.subject_id = t3.subject_id and ( datetime(t3.dod) between datetime(t2.charttime) and datetime(t2.charttime,'+2 month') ) or ( datetime(t2.charttime) between datetime(t3.dod) and datetime(t3.dod,'+2 month') )

value.diagnosis_name: diarrhea

tag: Count the number of patients who were dead after having been diagnosed with {diagnosis_name} [time_filter_within:within-n_month] [time_filter_global1:rel-year-last].

question: what is the three diagnoses which have the lowest four year survival rate?
template: what are the top three diagnoses that have the highest four year mortality rate?
query: select d_icd_diagnoses.long_title from d_icd_diagnoses where d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code in ( select t4.icd_code from ( select t3.icd_code, dense_rank() over ( order by t3.c1 desc ) as c2 from ( select t2.icd_code, 100 - sum( case when patients.dod is null then 1 when strftime('%j',patients.dod) - strftime('%j',t2.charttime) > 4 * 365 then 1 else 0 end ) * 100 / count(*) as c1 from ( select t1.subject_id, t1.icd_code, t1.charttime from ( select admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime from admissions join diagnoses_icd on admissions.hadm_id = diagnoses_icd.hadm_id group by admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code having min(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) as t1 where strftime('%j',current_time) - strftime('%j',t1.charttime) > 4 * 365 ) as t2 join patients on t2.subject_id = patients.subject_id group by t2.icd_code ) as t3 ) as t4 where t4.c2 <= 3 )
q_tag: what are the top [n_rank] diagnoses that have the highest [n_survival_period] mortality rate?
tag: What are the top [n_rank:three] diagnoses that have the highest [n_survival_period:four year] mortality rate?

query: select d_labitems.label from d_labitems where d_labitems.itemid in ( select t1.itemid from ( select labevents.itemid, dense_rank() over ( order by count(*) desc ) as c1 from labevents where labevents.hadm_id in ( select admissions.hadm_id from admissions where admissions.age between 50 and 59 ) and strftime('%y',labevents.charttime) = '2105' group by labevents.itemid ) as t1 where t1.c1 <= 4 )

question: what are the top five most frequent drugs that patients were prescribed with within 2 month after receiving angioplasty of other non-coronary vessel(s) in 2102?

query: select t3.drug from ( select t2.drug, dense_rank() over ( order by count(*) desc ) as c1 from ( select admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime from procedures_icd join admissions on procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id where procedures_icd.icd_code = ( select d_icd_procedures.icd_code from d_icd_procedures where d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'angioplasty of other non-coronary vessel(s)' ) and strftime('%y',procedures_icd.charttime) = '2102' ) as t1 join ( select admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime from prescriptions join admissions on prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id where strftime('%y',prescriptions.starttime) = '2102' ) as t2 on t1.subject_id = t2.subject_id where t1.charttime < t2.starttime and datetime(t2.starttime) between datetime(t1.charttime) and datetime(t1.charttime,'+2 month') group by t2.drug ) as t3 where t3.c1 <= 5

value.procedure_name: angioplasty of other non-coronary vessel(s)

question: what is the three year survival rate for a patient with irritable bowel syndrome?
template: what is the three year survival rate of patients diagnosed with irritable bowel syndrome?
query: select sum( case when patients.dod is null then 1 when strftime('%j',patients.dod) - strftime('%j',t2.charttime) > 3 * 365 then 1 else 0 end ) * 100 / count(*) from ( select t1.subject_id, t1.charttime from ( select admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime from diagnoses_icd join admissions on diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id where diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( select d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code from d_icd_diagnoses where d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'irritable bowel syndrome' ) group by admissions.subject_id having min(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) as t1 where strftime('%j',current_time) - strftime('%j',t1.charttime) > 3 * 365 ) as t2 join patients on t2.subject_id = patients.subject_id

value.diagnosis_name: irritable bowel syndrome

question: since 2101, what were the five most often ordered microbiology tests for patients who had previously been diagnosed with obstruction by bony pelvis during labor, delivered, with or without mention of antepartum condition within the same month?

query: select t3.test_name from ( select t2.test_name, dense_rank() over ( order by count(*) desc ) as c1 from ( select admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime from diagnoses_icd join admissions on diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id where diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( select d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code from d_icd_diagnoses where d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'obstruction by bony pelvis during labor, delivered, with or without mention of antepartum condition' ) and strftime('%y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= '2101' ) as t1 join ( select admissions.subject_id, microbiologyevents.test_name, microbiologyevents.charttime from microbiologyevents join admissions on microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id where strftime('%y',microbiologyevents.charttime) >= '2101' ) as t2 on t1.subject_id = t2.subject_id where t1.charttime < t2.charttime and datetime(t1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(t2.charttime,'start of month') group by t2.test_name ) as t3 where t3.c1 <= 5
